Class SystemAttributeHelper

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.BaseHelper
us.mn.state.dot.tms.SystemAttributeHelper
public class SystemAttributeHelper extends BaseHelper
Static System Attribute convenience methods accessible from the client and server. These methods are used to retrieve system attributes and validate them.
Author:
Michael Darter, Douglas Lau
